Fig 'Brown Turkey' produces a heavy crop of luscious, purple-skinned, pink-fleshed fruits, plus beautiful, sculptural leaves. Grows best planted against a south- or west-facing fence or wall. Plant it in a container or line a large planting hole with paving slabs to keep the roots well contained. Buy one three-litre bush-grown specimen for £24.95, or two for £39.90 (prices include UK mainland p&p). Call 0330 333 6851, quoting ref GUPW259 or visit our Reader Offers page. Delivery within 28 days.